{"tid":1625945,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"無人提呢兩樣有關兒童院既野好有問題?","createTime":"2019-10-05T09:03:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-10T15:02:54.000Z","uid":98710,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"8473e7b9bc3dd7bc6c874555d66d9e04441b5d5b","tid":1625945,"uid":98710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T09:03:00.000Z","msg":"<strong><br />\n1. 警察拉人, 要女性全裸搜身, 大家覺好大件事<br />\n但係一個無犯事無比人告既小朋友, 每次出入兒童院都要全裸搜身 <br />\n對一個小朋友心理影響都幾大<br />\n<br />\n2. 完全無視小朋友學習需要, 人地提到話上數學課但不被接納要人學化妝剪髮<br />\n如果入去係MK無心向學可能無問題, 但係保護令依家可能用到係一般學生到, 剝奪一個正常學生既學習機會係好有問題<br />\n</strong><br />\n<br />\n院童制服分「黃藍」 同色同住同生活<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/pns/%e8%a6%81%e8%81%9e/article/20190930/s00001/1569782635378/%e9%99%a2%e7%ab%a5%e5%88%b6%e6%9c%8d%e5%88%86%e3%80%8c%e9%bb%83%e8%97%8d%e3%80%8d-%e5%90%8c%e8%89%b2%e5%90%8c%e4%bd%8f%e5%90%8c%e7%94%9f%e6%b4%bb\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F%25e8%25a6%2581%25e8%2581%259e%2Farticle%2F20190930%2Fs00001%2F1569782635378%2F%25e9%2599%25a2%25e7%25ab%25a5%25e5%2588%25b6%25e6%259c%258d%25e5%2588%2586%25e3%2580%258c%25e9%25bb%2583%25e8%2597%258d%25e3%2580%258d-%25e5%2590%258c%25e8%2589%25b2%25e5%2590%258c%25e4%25bd%258f%25e5%2590%258c%25e7%2594%259f%25e6%25b4%25bb&d=cj%2BBBxPbgcFbNOKLHyO8KNXOzSaib9VKtZEsb4jNOpA%3D&h=f6db25e8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F%25e8%25a6%2581%25e8%2581%259e%2Farticle%2F20190930%2Fs00001%2F1569782635378%2F%25e9%2599%25a2%25e7%25ab%25a5%25e5%2588%25b6%25e6%259c%258d%25e5%2588%2586%25e3%2580%258c%25e9%25bb%2583%25e8%2597%258d%25e3%2580%258d-%25e5%2590%258c%25e8%2589%25b2%25e5%2590%258c%25e4%25bd%258f%25e5%2590%258c%25e7%2594%259f%25e6%25b4%25bb&h=23190e13\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/pns/%e8%a6%81%e8%81%9e/article/20190930/s00001/1569782635378/%e9%99%a2%e7%ab%a5%e5%88%b6%e6%9c%8d%e5%88%86%e3%80%8c%e9%bb%83%e8%97%8d%e3%80%8d-%e5%90%8c%e8%89%b2%e5%90%8c%e4%bd%8f%e5%90%8c%e7%94%9f%e6%b4%bb</a><br />\n<br />\n黃為保護令 藍正受審訊<br />\n受訪13歲女童阿妹（化名）表示，院童分為3種顏色的制服，紫色為被定罪、黃色為保護令、藍色為正接受審訊的院童，同一類院童會同住及生活。<span style=\"color: red;\">院童每次進入兒童院都需脫光衣服搜身</span>，隨行物品要放入儲物櫃，包括所有電子器材，而院舍內的職員全是社工。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20191001/60100357?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post&amp;fbclid=IwAR0jCvONtK-OevhB48RRUyOD5ee1tNCJ27opBLF81RLazuxIawqnNYUT_3A\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191001%2F60100357%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post%26fbclid%3DIwAR0jCvONtK-OevhB48RRUyOD5ee1tNCJ27opBLF81RLazuxIawqnNYUT_3A&d=cj%2BBBxPbgcFbNOKLHyO8KNXOzSaib9VKtZEsb4jNOpA%3D&h=3cf1f5e8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191001%2F60100357%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post%26fbclid%3DIwAR0jCvONtK-OevhB48RRUyOD5ee1tNCJ27opBLF81RLazuxIawqnNYUT_3A&h=5f9588b7\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20191001/60100357?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post&amp;fbclid=IwAR0jCvONtK-OevhB48RRUyOD5ee1tNCJ27opBLF81RLazuxIawqnNYUT_3A</a><br />\n談到兒童院的生活，<span style=\"color: red;\">Chim說她有向院舍提出希望上數學課但不被接納，「每日都上VTC堂，例如做手工，程度小學生都不如，或者係學化妝剪髮。我想追返我啲數學。」</span>阿妹則說兒童院與世隔絕，她每次只獲3分鐘時間致電親朋，也幾乎沒看過新聞。「飯堂日日淨係播旅遊節目同偶像劇；星期六、日先有康體時段，有半個鐘睇報紙。」阿妹指，因保護令而入住的院童穿黃色衣服，與等候審訊的藍色及已定罪的紫色衣服區分。其他院童曾告訴她，兩人進來後，院舍少播了新聞。"},{"pid":"2d7cae04fe9afa0c93bfe52ebcfb4947f79a5eb4","tid":1625945,"uid":16846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T09:13:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.g